83	// separate gain register: phase-state magnitude is encoded directly in
84	// bits [4:0] of the VM_I/VM_Q bytes above.  Per-channel VGA gain is a
85	// distinct register (CHx_RX_GAIN at 0x10-0x13, CHx_TX_GAIN at 0x1C-0x1F)
